%table#email-password(width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto; max-width:600px;")
	%tr
		%td(align="center" style="padding-top: 25px; padding-bottom: 25px;")
			= image_tag("logo.png", width: "263px", height:"34px", alt: "OptimizePlayer", style: "display:block;")
	%tr(bgcolor="#FFFFFF")
		%td(align="center" style="border-color: #d4e6e8; border-width: 2px 2px 0px 2px; border-style: solid; padding-top: 50px; border-top-right-radius:4px; border-top-left-radius:4px;")
			%span(style="color:#6996a9; font-size:28px; font-family:'HelveticaNeue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;") 
				Hi Tesha!
	%tr(bgcolor="#FFFFFF")
		%td(align="center" style="border-color: #d4e6e8; border-width: 0px 2px 0px 2px; border-style: solid; padding-top: 35px; padding-left: 45px; padding-right: 45px;")
			%span(style="color:#6996a9; font-size:18px; font-family:'HelveticaNeue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;")
				Someone has requested a link to change your password. You can do this by pressing the button bellow.
	%tr(bgcolor="#FFFFFF")
		%td(align="center" style="border-color: #d4e6e8; border-width: 0px 2px 0px 2px; border-style: solid; padding-top: 35px;")
			%a(href="#" style="color:#ffffff; font-size:30px; font-family:'HelveticaNeue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; background-color:#1ca8dd; text-decoration:none; border: 2px solid #148fbd; padding: 8px 21px; border-radius: 4px;")
				Change my password
	%tr(bgcolor="#FFFFFF")
		%td(align="center" style="border-color: #d4e6e8; border-width: 0px 2px 2px 2px; border-style: solid; padding-top: 45px; padding-left: 45px; padding-right: 45px; padding-bottom: 45px; border-bottom-right-radius:4px; border-bottom-left-radius:4px;")
			%span(style="color:#6996a9; font-size:18px; font-family:'HelveticaNeue',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;")
				If you didn’t request this, please ignore this email. Your password won’t change until you access the link above and create a new one.